{
  "id": "6a1a635d89b94e564d03625f",
  "title": "1が1つで任意の自然数が作れる",
  "created": 1780114271,
  "updated": 1780142460,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a1a635d89b94e564d03625f",
      "text": "1が1つで任意の自然数が作れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114271,
      "updated": 1780114271
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a635f00000000006a69a6",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b3efc8e225fc7269d2ec7c7fc4c7a82c]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114271,
      "updated": 1780114273
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a636000000000006a69a7",
      "text": "[$ \\exp\\left(\\exp\\left(-\\ln\\left(-\\ln\\left(\\sqrt{\\exp\\left(-\\exp\\left(-\\ln\\left(-\\ln\\left(\\cos\\left(\\arctan\\left(\\sqrt{n}\\right)\\right)\\right)\\right)\\right)\\right)}\\right)\\right)\\right)\\right)=n+1]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780114273,
      "updated": 1780117930
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a642100000000006a69ab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114465,
      "updated": 1780114465
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a642600000000006a69ad",
      "text": "X.comで見て、どういう仕組みか気になった[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114471,
      "updated": 1780114479
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a642600000000006a69ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114470,
      "updated": 1780114470
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a641e00000000006a69a9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/ba421f4283e4c8b56571a6c3447ed9de]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114462,
      "updated": 1780114464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a641f00000000006a69aa",
      "text": "\tなるほど[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114464,
      "updated": 1780114484
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a715b00000000003c8d42",
      "text": "\tピタゴラスってpythagorasって書くのか[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780117844,
      "updated": 1780117854
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a716400000000003c8d43",
      "text": "\t パイタゴラスって読んじゃった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780117854,
      "updated": 1780117862
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a643400000000006a69af",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114485,
      "updated": 1780114485
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a643400000000006a69b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114485,
      "updated": 1780114485
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a643400000000006a69ae",
      "text": "[$ \\cos(\\arctan(\\sqrt{n})) = {1\\over \\sqrt{1+x}}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114484,
      "updated": 1780115412
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a6800000000006a69e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116073,
      "updated": 1780116073
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a900000000006a69b1",
      "text": "↓ ln",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780116073
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a6700000000006a69e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116071,
      "updated": 1780116071
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a67fd00000000006a69b9",
      "text": "[$ -{1\\over 2} \\ln(1+x)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115453,
      "updated": 1780116071
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a6400000000006a69e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116068,
      "updated": 1780116068
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a67d600000000006a69b6",
      "text": "↓ -1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115414,
      "updated": 1780116068
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a6500000000006a69e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116070,
      "updated": 1780116070
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a682500000000006a69bb",
      "text": "[$ {1\\over 2} \\ln(1+x)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115493,
      "updated": 1780116070
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a682300000000006a69ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115491,
      "updated": 1780115880
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a68f000000000006a69c1",
      "text": "↓  exp(-ln( ))",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115697,
      "updated": 1780115708
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69ab00000000006a69c9",
      "text": "\t\tここでlnをやるのではなく [$ \\exp(-\\ln(x)) = 1/x] を使った方がわかりやすい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115883,
      "updated": 1780115884
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69ab00000000006a69ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115884,
      "updated": 1780115885
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a68f100000000006a69c2",
      "text": "[$ 2 {1\\over \\ln(1+x)}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115697,
      "updated": 1780115765
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a5e00000000006a69e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116062,
      "updated": 1780116062
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a692500000000006a69c3",
      "text": "↓ -1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115749,
      "updated": 1780116062
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a5d00000000006a69e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116061,
      "updated": 1780116061
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a695000000000006a69c4",
      "text": "[$ -2 {1\\over \\ln(1+x)}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115792,
      "updated": 1780115814
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a5a00000000006a69e1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116058,
      "updated": 1780116058
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a696300000000006a69c5",
      "text": "↓ exp",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780115811,
      "updated": 1780118380
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a5700000000006a69df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116055,
      "updated": 1780116055
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a697900000000006a69c6",
      "text": "[$ \\exp(-2 {1\\over \\ln(1+x)})]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115833,
      "updated": 1780116055
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a5800000000006a69e0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780116057,
      "updated": 1780116057
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a698b00000000006a69c7",
      "text": "↓ sqrt",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115852,
      "updated": 1780116057
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69a000000000006a69c8",
      "text": "\t\tsqrtすることでexpの中身が1/2倍される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115872,
      "updated": 1780115908
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69af00000000006a69cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115888,
      "updated": 1780115888
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69c800000000006a69cc",
      "text": "[$ \\exp(- {1\\over \\ln(1+x)})]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115912,
      "updated": 1780115916
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69c800000000006a69cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115912,
      "updated": 1780115912
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69d300000000006a69ce",
      "text": "↓ ln",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115924,
      "updated": 1780115931
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69dc00000000006a69d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115932,
      "updated": 1780115932
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69db00000000006a69cf",
      "text": "[$ - {1\\over \\ln(1+x)}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115931,
      "updated": 1780115943
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69e200000000006a69d2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115938,
      "updated": 1780115938
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69e200000000006a69d1",
      "text": "↓ -1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115938,
      "updated": 1780115955
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69f300000000006a69d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115955,
      "updated": 1780115955
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69f300000000006a69d5",
      "text": "[$ {1\\over \\ln(1+x)}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115955,
      "updated": 1780115962
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69f200000000006a69d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115955,
      "updated": 1780115955
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a69fa00000000006a69d6",
      "text": "↓ ln",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115963,
      "updated": 1780115994
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a1a00000000006a69d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780115994,
      "updated": 1780115994
    },
    {
